OL,3,CGrave of man who composed Welsh
OL,4,Cnational anthem restored
OL,6,FNow, ahead of the Eisteddfod coming to
OL,7,Ftheir hometown of Pontypridd next
OL,8,Fmonth, local people and businesses
OL,9,Fhave restored the grave to its former
OL,10,Fself.
OL,12,FAngharad Walters was one of them.
OL,14,F"I thought that with the Eisteddfod
OL,15,Fbeing in Ponty, that now would be a
OL,16,Fgreat time to do the renovation, so we
OL,17,Fcould celebrate our anthem and pay our
OL,18,Frespects to essentially one of the
OL,19,Fmost important people in Welsh
OL,20,Fhistory." she said.
