OL,4,Cnational anthem restored
OL,6,FBusinesses in Aberdare paid for the
OL,7,Frestoration which was carried out by
OL,8,FIvor Phillips Sculptors and Angharad
OL,9,Fhopes the new grave will boost
OL,10,Fvisitors to the town.
OL,12,FThe song we now know as Hen Wlad was
OL,13,Foriginally called Glan Rhondda. It's
OL,14,Fsaid the tune came into the older
OL,15,FJames' mind while walking the bank of
OL,16,Fthe river Rhondda.
