OL,6,FThe song's popularity began to rise
OL,7,Fwhen it was sang at 19th century
OL,8,FEisteddfodau. It is also said to be
OL,9,Fthe first anthem sung at an
OL,10,Finternational sporting event.
OL,12,F"This is probably one of the proudest
OL,13,Fthings I've ever been part of,"
OL,14,FAngharad said.
OL,16,FShe continued: "I am over the moon.
OL,17,FI'm from Maesteg originally and the
OL,18,Fanthem was first sang there so I am
OL,19,Fsuper proud to have played a small
OL,20,Fpart in getting it restored to its
OL,21,Fformer glory.
